The post focuses on Dumea's professional achievements and the project's merits, not on influencing electoral choices.</electoral-objective>

<post_id>1003257334091817</post_id>
<electoral-propaganda-analysis>
The Facebook post does not constitute electoral propaganda.  The post focuses on a non-political project, the "Ghidul Digitalizării," and Bogdan Dumea's role in its development. While Dumea is affiliated with the PSD, the post does not advocate for his candidacy or any other candidate in the parliamentary elections. The content is informative and does not attempt to influence voters' choices.  The fact that it's a paid advertisement does not automatically make it electoral propaganda; the content itself must meet the criteria for such classification.  In this case, it does not.
